                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/1540" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">MKT-0245</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8907 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">广之旅：线上和线下营销渠道整合</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">GZL International Travel Service： Integration of online and offline marketing channel</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">梁彦明，江向华</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">暨南大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">广州广之旅国际旅行社股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">26 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销渠道；线上渠道； 线下渠道； 渠道整合； O2O</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">marketing channels; online channel; offline channel; channel integration; O2O</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例刻画了广之旅在线上和线下营销渠道整合过程中所面对的复杂决策情境。广之旅是华南地区最大的旅行社，公司过去主要通过线下实体门店销售旅游产品。近年来，为了适应旅游市场的在线化和散客化趋势，公司积极开展渠道创新，开辟线上营销渠道，线上销售收入已达总收入的10%。与此同时，线上线下两类营销渠道定位不明朗、分工不清晰、运作上缺乏互补和协同等问题也逐渐凸显。广之旅拟利用IT系统重建的契机对线上线下渠道进行整合，这不仅是营销层面的问题，还涉及对公司业务模式（客户定位、产品形态和批零结构等）的调整。本案例全面描述了问题产生的复杂背景，提供了公司解决问题的基本思路和面临的一些困惑，以期引发人们对服务企业线上线下营销渠道整合问题的讨论。
</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">This case depicts a complex decision situations that company leaders of GZL facing during the integration of online and offline marketing channels.
GZL is the largest travel agency in Southern China. In the past, the company sells travel products mainly through the physical stores. In recent years, in order to adapt to the consumption trends of independent and online travel arrangement,GZL implements channel innovation actively,expansion marketing channels from offline to online,online sales revenue has reached 10% of total revenue. At the same time, positioning uncertainty, unclear of functions division, lack of complementarity and synergies and other operational issues between online and offline marketing channels are also increasingly prominent. Use the opportunity to rebuild the IT systems, GZL intends to integrate online and offline channels. Integration of marketing channels involves not only the marketing problem, but also adjustments of company&#39;s business model (include customer orientation, product form, and wholesale and retail structure, etc.) .This case describes the comprehensive background of the above-mentioned problems, introduced the company&#39;s basic idea of decision-making on this issue, and describes some of the confusion that GZL facing.
This case expectations leading people to discuss the channel innovation and online- offline channel integration issues of service companies.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2013</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《市场营销》、《旅游市场营销》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">线上和线下营销渠道、O2O 的三个层次：渠道叠加、渠道整合和渠道融合</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2014-05</td>
                            </tr>
